item.title: ‘SNL’ Alum Laraine Newman Reacts to Cast Shake-Up, Says Her Era Was “When Lorne Didn’t Fire People”
item.description: The original ‘Saturday Night Live’ castmember talks to The Hollywood Reporter about the cast exits ahead of season 51: “I was very sad to see Michael Longfellow go.”
